Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:56.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,何処までも行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.90,EDJP_S,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1798,10)}ゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:03.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,諦めなきゃ∞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.36,EDJP_S,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1906,10)}むげんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:13.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不安なんておやつにして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,回り道だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:18.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,たどり着けば正解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:22.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,考えるよりも先に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心は動いちゃうから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:30.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,予定調和なんてありえないんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:34.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,セメント色したビルも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:38.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不機嫌すぎる空でも全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:43.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君が笑えば思い出になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:47.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心の容量いっぱいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:50.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,保存した思いを力に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:53.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,理想と違う現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:56.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,足がすくんじゃうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:00.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心の中にあるコンパスは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,知っている　指し示している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:06.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,何が待っているかは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:09.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,進む未知の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:12.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,進む道の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:14.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまでも行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:14.91,EDJP_S,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1798,10)}ゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:15.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:56.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,千里之行　始於足下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,天涯海角　皆是通途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:03.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,若不放棄便有無盡可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:13.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,將不安當作開胃的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,即便百轉千回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:18.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,抵達終點便是正途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:22.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,思考尚未開始反應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳已經怦然加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:30.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,預定？配合？根本無從談起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:34.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無論水泥色的單調大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:38.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,還是惹人不快天空等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:43.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有你笑容便是珍貴回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:47.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,留存心間時時滿溢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:50.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,思念化作無盡動力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:53.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,理想現實落差懸殊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:56.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,令人不禁停步駐足
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:00.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,心中的那枚指南針
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,從不迷惘直指前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:06.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,且問有何相待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:09.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,盡在未知前方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:12.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,盡在通途彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:14.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,天涯海角　攜手共赴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:15.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//zheng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼就篤悠悠地泡起溫泉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為平時想洗也很難找到機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說遊擊隊四處奔波什麼最苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用想嗎　就是沒法每天洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這種時候肯定毫不猶豫囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…泥胎族？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和它們戰鬥都比不上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擬態族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涅伊特上弄個淋浴多好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是露營房車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相應的不是能洗衣服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相應的能洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倆能相應得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能穿上乾淨衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總還能湊合湊合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個情況還真是出乎預料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過感覺也做得有板有眼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是時空震的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣　雖然沒去成理子要去的所澤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但直接通到山梨也確實意外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通到…是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是空間扭曲了的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時空震之後總會有所變化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至於何時能恢復就不得而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是說我回不去所澤了的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便我們抵達了這個世界的所澤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡也不會是你口中的那個所澤了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我這輩子都回不了家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個問題沒有人能夠斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少現在沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼就她自己泡暈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一直哭個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是脫水症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來她在原來的世界過得很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡應該離陸防富士教導團不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯繫那邊確認一下最新組織情況和今後的行動方針吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便找個地方買點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用新搞到的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸　媽媽　椋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了　理子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有認真作過自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像確實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我已經記住大家的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的　我很擅長認人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家開咖啡館的　有很多老主顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫叫看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.30,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}杏花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:53.76,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.91,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.17,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}美春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒一個叫對的還行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦　搞錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是自以為記住了結果搞錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫由衣　瀧藤由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家住在叫「調布」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挨著一個叫「深大寺」的寺廟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱原杏花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自橫濱市青葉區
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒環鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家住千葉的幕張
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久留木美春　東京檜原…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京？東京哪裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澀谷？原宿？台場？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在東京很西邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊　西武線能到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說理子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調布也算東京哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎　西武線能到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那邊的調布沒通電車…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也重新自我介紹下　森澤理子　所澤…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熔岩台地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因以前富士山噴發的岩漿流過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在地下形成了廣闊的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才地面崩塌也是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空洞一方面可以讓市民避難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也是天然的倉儲空間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這御殿場的地理環境作為抵禦擬態族的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以說是最佳選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然有坑你倒是說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給句話啊　涅伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能說誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地形探測模式沒有開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常都會自動設置才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由衣小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只能說你的認知出現了些許偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我這樣　操作方面基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是手動的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個模式在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我狠狠地把它打開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是裝甲少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼立在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為保衛這據點戰死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有裝甲少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝甲少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來也對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到裝甲爺們的話就讓他們做三倍的活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯　索性塗成紅色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝甲爺們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去打水　買方便食品和應急口糧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有零食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野和美春去買日用品和衛生用品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗滌劑要買無需晾曬的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整備用的套筒好像有磨損了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實　要是有3/4和7/8的就買回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便再買一個棘輪扳手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以也挑幾樣零食嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的口味和我還蠻接近的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理子和我去買食物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單獨結帳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說　你怎麼還拿這玩意到處跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不用現金嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種紙幣已經沒有價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是用那種…電子錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種也不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核心水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這裡那就是錢的代用品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就是這個世界的能量來源物質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對擬態族而言核心也是生命之源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們裝甲少女也是仰仗核心的力量戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並從擬態族那裡奪取核心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核心水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是使用核心的發電廠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道到底是打算怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是聽說阻止第二次時空震失敗了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有傳聞說防衛隊和裝甲少女都全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京的擬態族都要漫出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去參加作戰的自衛團也還沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良介和弘樹怎麼樣了　太一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說很多據點都被拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不是也應該從這裡撤離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拋棄這裡還能去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是自衛團該考慮的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是裝甲少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有五位吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝甲少女哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是池袋的倖存者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遊擊隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不快去簽下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾位莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客氣　盡情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃　我開動…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準確來說不是全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依我們提前從陸防那裡得到的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第二次時空震阻止作戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面作戰的戰力損耗為40%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防衛隊自不待言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各地自衛團　各個裝甲少女部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分也已經喪失了作戰能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正重新編組中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各地有據點被拋棄似乎也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家要放棄這裡還為時過早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被熔岩台地包圍的御殿場作為據點可謂是佔據了地利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說支援部隊因為時空扭曲而不能按時到達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前殘存戰力也都在返回各個據點的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜候方為上策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的人已經回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在池袋為我們殿後的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的標誌和那個一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未查實情空口白話非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧他們我們才能保全性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊　這結局也很有他們的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會讓他們白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說完全沒有以此事強求你們還人情的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你們可否稍作停留助我們一臂之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉　容我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包含我們在內的遊擊戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有著保衛據點以外的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說遊擊隊人數已所剩不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是確認到了因第二次時空震
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有新的裝甲少女轉移到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在需要搜索新的來訪者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須和防衛隊以及各地的研究所進行聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　那良介和弘樹就白白犧牲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了救你們這些白眼狼才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說我們白眼狼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我們想這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也是隸屬於組織的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在當前狀況下　並不能擅自下判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少給我扯大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠我們同伴的犧牲才苟活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你們說得出這種話來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我　我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃相太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要為了自己的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她們一直戰鬥到死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把核心存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在盡力想辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在擬態族劇增的時候　以防萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不都一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是遲早而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時再在廣場立新的銅像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　你想要的話就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此　還望能夠理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自第六瞭望塔的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西南偏西方向有擬態族接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認三隊小型…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家　出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勞煩各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在滯留期間我們會應對…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電力系統功率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匿蹤模式　倒數一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度的應對是完全沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加強周邊的電磁護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過降低城鎮主電源的核心部分的功率
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使擬態族迷失目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法減少它們的數量就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說　杏花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否進入陸防的管轄下  是遵循個人意願的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在這裡幫他們一把也可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟對我們有恩在先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是趕走擬態族的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儲存的核心早晚會消耗殆盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是他們自己的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以據點等級來考慮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只是飲鴆止渴罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但哪裡也都差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了　鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話　這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你很想吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強忍可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才該道謝　方才為我們說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是剛加入的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道這裡的人為我們犧牲時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對她們說的話很是在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又不是我這個昨天才加入的人該插嘴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是昨天　其實是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都只想著自己能活下來就萬事大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是裝甲少女的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是該自己決定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理子你真會做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了　在店裡幫忙的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一點點的學會了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想每天都吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的哦　我很喜歡做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃是好吃　但是不計後果地用了太多食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說現在剛進行了一波補給沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要為了長時間不能補給的情況考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你每天都做飯的話就更加要斟酌一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一臉幸福樣完全沒說服力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是太好吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先出…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.34,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.34,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.34,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}錛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.34,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(15,15)}Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.34,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始不該是石頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說是布吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧　是石頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:18:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了是布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說了錛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錛　鉸　裹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.14,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(852,1000)}Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.14,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,1000)}Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.14,Default_zhu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070,1000)}Five
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從沒聽說過這叫法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一直都得不出結論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以都不管什麼規矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭　剪刀　布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了　美春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是睡的地方的話　接受那些人的好意該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡那真是很難睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去洗下盤子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說　已經分好陣地了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前不是已經定下規矩只要有三個人就可以先決定了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒水出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了補充生活用水了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能要打擊你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那片星空裡有著擬態族的母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為被它們掌控了制空權
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空運和高空中的戰術都無法實行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制…制空權？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂的話不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不單只是這裡　選擇隸屬於哪個組織戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話　還沒有正式戰鬥過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為這樣才更想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不久之後可能會毀滅的這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要怎樣活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是完全摸不著方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才　自衛團的大哥哥對我說這是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為裝甲少女該決定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女孩也一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為保衛據點的人們挺身而出奮戰到了最後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為裝甲少女轉移到這個世界沒有多久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是自願來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算逃走都絕不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要問想做什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尋找回到原來世界的所澤的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話你便無法逃離來自擬態族的威脅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有想過說不定明天就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完成了哦　彩香
